Provider terms & data usage
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

VulcanBench is an independent evaluation harness. It is not affiliated with,
sponsored by, or endorsed by any model provider.

- Bring your own keys. VulcanBench never bundles or shares API credentials.
  Each run is made under your own account and your own commercial/API agreement
  with the provider, using the keys in your environment. You are responsible for
  complying with your provider's terms and usage policies.

- Outputs are for evaluation, not training. Recorded run artifacts (traces,
  patches, summaries) capture model outputs solely for scoring, inspection, and
  reproducibility. OpenAI and Anthropic prohibit using their outputs to develop
  or train competing AI models; do not use VulcanBench artifacts, or any
  published corpus of them, for that purpose.

